
##### Maven command to create a new Java project named sbi-app:-

mvn archetype:generate \
  -DgroupId=com.sbi.app \
  -DartifactId=sbi-app \
  -DarchetypeArtifactId=maven-archetype-quickstart \
  -DinteractiveMode=false


